{"ID":270280, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"280\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs279.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs281.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 280<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">that he has seen the sign of the Son of Man as foretold in the 24th chapter of Matthew.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The slanderous allusion of a &ldquo;seraglio&rdquo; like the Grand Turk, which the editor applies to me, he\n  may take to himself, for, &ldquo;out of the abundance of the heart the mouth speaketh.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> Every honest man\n  who has visited the city of Nauvoo since it existed, can bear record of better things, and place me\n  in the front ranks of those who are known to do good for the sake of goodness, and show all liars,\n  hypocrites<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> and abominable creatures that, while vice sinks them down to darkness<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> and woe, virtue\n  exalts me and the Saints to light and immortality.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The editor, as well as some others, &ldquo;thinks that Joe Smith has his match at last,&rdquo; because Mr.\n  Redding thinks that he has seen the sign of the Son of Man. But I shall use my right, and declare\n  that, notwithstanding Mr. Redding may have seen a wonderful appearance in the clouds one morning\n  about sunrise (which is nothing very uncommon in the winter season) he has not seen the sign of the\n  Son of Man, as foretold by Jesus;<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> neither has any man, nor will any man, until after the sun shall\n  have been darkened and the moon bathed in blood;<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> for the Lord hath not shown me any such sign;<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span>\n  and as the prophet saith, so it must be&mdash;&ldquo;Surely the Lord God will do nothing, but He revealeth His\n  secret unto His servants the prophets.&rdquo; (See Amos 3:7.)<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> Therefore, hear this, O earth:<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> The Lord\n  will not come to reign over the righteous, in this world, in 1843, nor until everything for the\n  Bridegroom is ready.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Yours respectfully,<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">JOSEPH SMITH.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">(Feb. 28, 1843.) DHC 5:290-291.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Battle of Gog and Magog<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The battle of Gog and Magog will be after the millennium.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> The remnant of all the nations that\n  fight against Jerusalem<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> were commanded to go up to Jerusalem to worship in the millennium.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span>\n  (March 4, 1843.)  DHC 5:298.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Giving Blessings a Tax on Strength<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Elder Jedediah M. Grant enquired of me the cause of my turning pale and losing strength last\n  night while blessing children.<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> I told him that I saw that Lucifer<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> would exert his influ-<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108220\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108220)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108220)\">Matt. 24:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107979\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107979)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107979)\">Matt. 12:34<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114241\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114241)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114241)\">D&amp;C 64:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107639\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107639)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107639)\">Amos 5:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110038\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110038)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110038)\">2 Tim. 1:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108221\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108221)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108221)\">Matt. 24:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107620\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107620)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107620)\">Joel 2:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113526\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113526)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113526)\">D&amp;C 29:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114890\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114890)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114890)\">D&amp;C 88:87-93<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116262\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116262)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116262)\">D&amp;C 130:14-15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107635\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107635)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107635)\">Amos 3:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106339\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106339)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106339)\">Deut. 32:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107000\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107000)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107000)\">Isa. 1:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107321\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107321)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107321)\">Jer. 6:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114369\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114369)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114369)\">D&amp;C 76:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116469\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116469)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116469)\">D&amp;C 133:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108236\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108236)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108236)\">Matt. 25:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113591\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113591)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113591)\">D&amp;C 33:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114255\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114255)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114255)\">D&amp;C 65:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"124521\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 124521)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(124521)\">Ezek. 38:1-23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"124522\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 124522)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(124522)\">Ezek. 39:1-29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110857\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110857)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110857)\">Rev. 20:8-9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111242\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111242)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111242)\">2 Ne. 25:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107714\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107714)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107714)\">Zech. 14:12-19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108350\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108350)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108350)\">Mark 10:13-16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112633\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112633)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112633)\">3 Ne. 17:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107067\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107067)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107067)\">Isa. 14:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114409\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114409)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114409)\">D&amp;C 76:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}